description: Zilda Williams is known for appearing on one episode of The Bachelor in 2015. Now she is posing for Instagram snaps in low cut bikinis while flaunting her ample cleavage to her 45k followers.
title: Zilda Williams flaunts her cleavage in low-cut swimsuit
title_page: Zilda Williams flaunts her cleavage in low-cut swimsuit | Daily Mail Online
text:
She's known for showing off her fantastic figure on Instagram.
And Zilda Williams was back at it on Friday, sharing more photos of her enviable body at a trendy pool party.
The buxom blonde stripped down to a one-piece swimsuit, sticking to her well-honed tradition of uploading sultry shots in skimpy swimwear.
Water baby: Zilda posed in the pool showing off her ample cleavage to her Instagram followers
Zilda looked sensational in the picture, as she posed in a swimming pool looking naturally tanned.
The 33-year-old glamour model wore an embellished Bella Bikini one-piece that barely contained her ample assets.
The navy-blue costume had bronze and turquoise embellishment along the bust-line, while the material hugged her curves.
All smiles: The gorgeous star appeared on the third season of The Bachelor
Her damp blonde hair was parted on the side and left out to flow over her shoulders and into the water.
She accessorised her ensemble with silver sunglasses that reflected the blue water of the pool.
Zilda captioned the photo with 'I'm such a water baby' and has racked up over 300 likes.
Beach babe: Zilda posts photos of her modeling swimwear to her 45k Instagram followers
Zilda first shot to fame after appearing on season three of The Bachelor contestant and was famously the first to be sent home by Sam Wood.
After becoming a fan-favourite in her short-lived time on the show, Zilda dedicated her life to her modelling and acting career.
She famously posts racy photos of herself on Instagram and has over 45,000 followers.
